title: Dollar Dollar Bill, Ya'll
description:
Mina and USA Today's Steven Ruiz answer free agency related mailbag questions about the Patriots spending spree, the Chiefs bolstering their offensive line, and the Bucs keeping everyone. Plus, they offer instant reactions to a flurry of deals that were reported during the taping of the podcast.
